      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       scl-pvg-vix-410.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Inizializzazione indice 1..1            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-scl-pvg-wvi-ioc      .
       scl-pvg-vix-420.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento indice 1..1                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
